verses.verse: יְהוָ֣ה <WH3068> The LORD מָלָךְ֮ <WH4427> reigneth גֵּא֪וּת <WH1348> with majesty לָ֫בֵ֥שׁ <WH3847> he is clothed לָבֵ֣שׁ <WH3847> is clothed יְ֭הוָה <WH3068> the LORD עֹ֣ז <WH5797> with strength הִתְאַזָּ֑ר <WH247> [wherewith] he hath girded אַף־ <WH637> Indeed תִּכּ֥וֹן <WH3559> also is stablished תֵּ֝בֵ֗ל <WH8398> himself the world בַּל־ <WH1077> lest תִּמּֽוֹט׃ <WH4131> that it cannot be moved
נָכ֣וֹן <WH3559> [is] established כִּסְאֲךָ֣ <WH3678> Thy throne מֵאָ֑ז <WH227> of old מֵֽעוֹלָ֣ם <WH5769> thou [art] from everlasting אָֽתָּה׃ <WH859> you

נָשְׂא֤וּ <WH5375> have lifted up נְהָר֨וֹת ׀ <WH5104> The floods יְֽהוָ֗ה <WH3068> O LORD נָשְׂא֣וּ <WH5375> have lifted up נְהָר֣וֹת <WH5104> the floods קוֹלָ֑ם <WH6963> their voice יִשְׂא֖וּ <WH5375> lift up נְהָר֣וֹת <WH5104> the floods דָּכְיָֽם׃ <WH1796> their waves

מִקֹּל֨וֹת ׀ <WH6963> than the noise מַ֤יִם <WH4325> waters רַבִּ֗ים <WH7227> of many אַדִּירִ֣ים <WH117> [is] mightier מִשְׁבְּרֵי־ <WH4867> waves יָ֑ם <WH3220> of the sea אַדִּ֖יר <WH117> [yea than] the mighty בַּמָּר֣וֹם <WH4791> on high יְהוָֽה׃ <WH3068> The LORD

עֵֽדֹתֶ֨יךָ ׀ <WH5713> Thy testimonies נֶאֶמְנ֬וּ <WH539> sure מְאֹ֗ד <WH3966> are very לְבֵיתְךָ֥ <WH1004> thine house נַאֲוָה־ <WH4998> becometh קֹ֑דֶשׁ <WH6944> holiness יְ֝הוָ֗ה <WH3068> O LORD לְאֹ֣רֶךְ <WH753> forever יָמִֽים׃ <WH3117> age
